    <input type="text" id="user-input" placeholder="‡∏û‡∏¥‡∏°‡∏û‡πå‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏°‡∏∂‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢...">
    <button onclick="sendMessage()">‡∏™‡πà‡∏á</button>
